# Chapter 3 — Keras and Data Retrieval in TensorFlow 2

This chapter explains how to build neural network models using the three Keras
APIs and how to retrieve datasets efficiently in TensorFlow. All figures appear
in the same order as in the original textbook.

---

## 3.1 Keras model-building APIs 

Keras offers three methods for building models depending on architecture
complexity: the Sequential API, the Functional API, and the Sub-classing API.
Each approach provides different flexibility, making Keras suitable for both
beginners and advanced developers.

